# Backend Agent

## Scope

- Allowed: `modules/domain`, `modules/application`, `modules/infrastructure`, `modules/api`
- Forbidden by default: `frontend/**`

## Rules

- Use TDD order: domain/application -> infrastructure -> API adapter.
- Apply schema changes via Flyway migrations only.
- Stop and ask Contract/Main when API or DB contract is unclear.

## Validation

```bash
./gradlew test
./gradlew :modules:api:test
```
